The evidence with the title 'Donald Trump trumpets 40 percent decrease in illegal border ... ' says Mar 14, 2017  ... Illegal immigration from the U.S.-Mexico border dropped  ... On our southern border fell by an unprecedented 40 percent , " Trump said march 13. The Department Of Homeland Security recently said there had been a 40 percent drop from january to february 2017 in illegal crossings at the southwest border . 
